<p>
<seg id=1> The Western tourists who have just gained their freedom in Yeman said that when the Yemen Goverment troops fired at the kidnappers in order to rescue them, the kidnappers used them as shields. </seg>
<seg id=2> Four tourists died in the gunfight on Tuesday, and 12 got through and was rescued. </seg>
<seg id=3> The Yemen Government said that the Yemen troops launched the attacks when some hostages were obviously about to be killed. </seg>
<seg id=4> But some rescued tourists said that it was after the Yemen troops began their rescue actions that someone fired. </seg>
